I'll explain when you're older,

928
01:03:02,690 --> 01:03:03,820
鹰眼
Hawkeye.

929
01:03:03,860 --> 01:03:05,530
好吧
Well, okay.

930
01:03:07,410 --> 01:03:08,990
情况不妙吧
It's bad, right?

931
01:03:09,120 --> 01:03:10,780
小娜好像很受伤
Nat seems really shaken.

932
01:03:11,700 --> 01:03:13,200
奥创有两个盟友
Ultron has these allies.

933
01:03:13,370 --> 01:03:17,420
两个孩子  都是小流氓
These kids. They're punks, really.

934
01:03:18,880 --> 01:03:21,380
他们拿了根特别大的棍子
But they carry a big, damn stick.

935
01:03:21,460 --> 01:03:22,960
小娜挨了挺重的一下
And Nat took a serious hit.

936
01:03:24,050 --> 01:03:26,510
得有人教训教训他们
Someone's gonna have to teach them some manners.

937
01:03:26,630 --> 01:03:28,390
那个人就是你吗
That someone being you.

938
01:03:29,850 --> 01:03:32,720
你当复仇者我非常支持
You know I totally support your Avenging.

939
01:03:32,770 --> 01:03:34,680
我无比自豪
I couldn't be prouder.

940
01:03:36,190 --> 01:03:37,480
但我看到他们...
But I see those guys...

941
01:03:37,600 --> 01:03:39,690
神一样的...
Those gods...

942
01:03:41,610 --> 01:03:43,900
你觉得他们不需要我
You don't think they need me.

943
01:03:44,070 --> 01:03:47,740
我觉得他们需要  这样更可怕
I think they do, which is a lot scarier.

944
01:03:48,860 --> 01:03:50,070
他们问题真是多啊
They're a mess.

945
01:03:51,660 --> 01:03:52,660
是啊
Yeah.

946
01:03:53,410 --> 01:03:55,160
那也是我的问题
I guess they're my mess.

947
01:03:56,410 --> 01:03:58,420
你得确保
You need to be sure

948
01:03:58,460 --> 01:04:01,090
团队能合作下去
that this team is really a team,

949
01:04:01,170 --> 01:04:03,090
能时刻支持你
and that they have your back.

950
01:04:06,300 --> 01:04:08,930
我们的日子也要变了
Things are changing for us.

951
01:04:08,970 --> 01:04:11,470
再过几个月
In a few months' time,

952
01:04:11,550 --> 01:04:14,350
孩子就要比大人多了
you and me are gonna be outnumbered.

953
01:04:14,430 --> 01:04:15,770
我得...
I need...

954
01:04:18,940 --> 01:04:20,770
一定要确保
Just be sure.

955
01:04:21,560 --> 01:04:23,070
遵命
Yes, ma'am.

956
01:04:32,120 --> 01:04:34,030
我能感觉到不一样
I can feel the difference.

957
01:04:36,620 --> 01:04:40,500
{\an8}韩国  首尔  尤金基因实验室

958
01:04:47,090 --> 01:04:49,760
敢出声  你的员工都得死
Scream, and your entire staff dies.

959
01:04:51,640 --> 01:04:53,970
我本可以杀了你  海伦  刚见面那晚
I could've killed you, Helen, the night we met.

960
01:04:54,050 --> 01:04:55,180
但我没有
I didn't.

961
01:04:55,260 --> 01:04:56,850
是要我谢你吗
Do you expect a thank-you note?

962
01:04:56,970 --> 01:04:58,730
我要你知道为什么
I expect you to know why.

963
01:04:59,850 --> 01:05:00,850
再生摇篮
The Cradle.

964
01:05:01,350 --> 01:05:03,400
这就是未来  托尼
This is the next thing, Tony.

965
01:05:03,480 --> 01:05:06,610
这就是未来的我
This is the next me.

966
01:05:06,730 --> 01:05:09,450
再生摇篮能生成组织
The Regeneration Cradle prints tissue.

967
01:05:09,490 --> 01:05:11,160
可造不出活的躯体
It can't build a living body.

968
01:05:11,280 --> 01:05:12,320
可以  你可以
It can. You can.

969
01:05:12,820 --> 01:05:14,200
你只是缺少材料
You lack the materials.

970
01:05:16,490 --> 01:05:17,950
你很厉害  海伦
You're a brilliant woman, Helen.

971
01:05:21,000 --> 01:05:24,670
但大家都有进步的空间
But we all have room to improve.

972
01:05:45,900 --> 01:05:48,530
我不知道你在等着
I didn't realize you were waiting.

973
01:05:48,570 --> 01:05:49,570
我想跟你一起洗来着
I would've joined you,

974
01:05:49,650 --> 01:05:53,030
但是好像时机不太对
but it didn't seem like the right time.

975
01:05:53,910 --> 01:05:56,200
热水被他们用光了
They used up all the hot water.

976
01:05:56,870 --> 01:05:58,290
真该跟你一起洗
I should've joined you.

977
01:05:58,410 --> 01:06:00,200
错过了机会
Missed our window.

978
01:06:00,870 --> 01:06:02,210
是吗
Did we?

979
01:06:05,710 --> 01:06:07,630
世界看到了绿巨人
The world just saw the Hulk.

980
01:06:09,420 --> 01:06:11,380
第一次见到了真正的绿巨人
The real Hulk, for the first time.

981
01:06:14,550 --> 01:06:15,550
你知道我得离开
You know I have to leave.

982
01:06:15,720 --> 01:06:17,260
你是觉得我应该留下吗
You assume that I have to stay?

983
01:06:19,220 --> 01:06:21,930
我做了个梦
I had this dream.

984
01:06:22,390 --> 01:06:24,400
做梦的时候觉得挺正常
The kind that seems normal at the time,

985
01:06:25,230 --> 01:06:26,900
但等醒了...
but when you wake...

986
01:06:26,980 --> 01:06:28,400
你梦见什么了
What did you dream?

987
01:06:29,400 --> 01:06:31,240
我是复仇者
That I was an Avenger.

988
01:06:33,070 --> 01:06:37,070
不只是他们一手打造的刺客
That I was anything more than the assassin they made me.

989
01:06:38,490 --> 01:06:40,660
你对自己太狠[硬]了
I think you're being hard on yourself.

990
01:06:42,660 --> 01:06:45,250
这不是你该干的吗
Here I was hoping that was your job.

991
01:06:48,130 --> 01:06:49,750
你干什么
What are you doing?

992
01:06:51,380 --> 01:06:53,220
顺其自然
I'm running with it.

993
01:06:54,430 --> 01:06:56,140
和你一起
With you.

994
01:06:56,800 --> 01:06:59,220
如果你打算走
If running is the plan,

995
01:07:00,260 --> 01:07:02,100
想去哪去哪
as far as you want.

996
01:07:03,930 --> 01:07:05,770
你疯了吗
Are you out of your mind?

997
01:07:10,980 --> 01:07:12,480
我希望你明白...
I want you to understand that...

998
01:07:12,570 --> 01:07:14,110
娜塔莎
Natasha,

999
01:07:15,070 --> 01:07:16,570
我能去哪
where can I go?

1000
01:07:17,610 --> 01:07:19,870
我到哪不是个祸害
Where in the world am I not a threat?

1001
01:07:19,990 --> 01:07:22,370
-在我这不是  -你确定吗
- You're not a threat to me. - Are you sure?

1002
01:07:23,250 --> 01:07:25,000
哪怕我没...
Even if I didn't just...

1003
01:07:26,670 --> 01:07:28,210
跟着我没有未来的
There's no future with me.

1004
01:07:29,750 --> 01:07:30,750
我不能...
I can't ever...

1005
01:07:30,920 --> 01:07:33,300
我不可能这样
I can't have this.

1006
01:07:33,960 --> 01:07:35,300
有孩子
Kids.

1007
01:07:35,420 --> 01:07:38,180
你自己想想  我是真的不能
Do the math. I physically can't.

1008
01:07:39,800 --> 01:07:41,350
我也不能
Neither can I.

1009
01:07:45,980 --> 01:07:49,560
我受训的那个红屋子里...
In the Red Room where I was trained...

1010
01:07:49,980 --> 01:07:52,520
我长大的地方
where I was raised,

1011
01:07:53,440 --> 01:07:56,110
有个毕业典礼
they have a graduation ceremony.

1012
01:07:57,700 --> 01:07:59,570
就是做绝育
They sterilize you.

1013
01:08:02,700 --> 01:08:04,200
效果很好
It's efficient.

1014
01:08:07,040 --> 01:08:08,580
少了件操心的事
One less thing to worry about.

1015
01:08:10,500 --> 01:08:13,960
唯一一件可能比任务还重要的事
The one thing that might matter more than a mission.

1016
01:08:16,300 --> 01:08:18,220
一切都简单多了
Makes everything easier.

1017
01:08:19,510 --> 01:08:20,930
哪怕是杀人
Even killing.

1018
01:08:25,850 --> 01:08:29,020
你还以为队伍里就你一个怪物吗
You still think you're the only monster on the team?

1019
01:08:35,150 --> 01:08:37,280
我们一起隐居吗
So, we disappear?

1020
01:08:43,700 --> 01:08:45,620
托尔没说他去哪找答案了吗
Thor didn't say where he was going for answers?

1021
01:08:46,580 --> 01:08:49,160
我的队员也不总跟我畅所欲言的
Sometimes my teammates don't tell me things.

1022
01:08:50,080 --> 01:08:52,540
我还希望托尔能对我敞开胸襟呢
I was kind of hoping Thor would be the exception.

1023
01:08:52,710 --> 01:08:54,420
给他点时间
Yeah, give him time.

1024
01:08:54,500 --> 01:08:56,670
我们不知道马克西莫夫给他看了什么
We don't know what the Maximoff kid showed him.

1025
01:08:58,590 --> 01:09:00,260
"地球上最强大的英雄组合"
"Earth's mightiest heroes."

1026
01:09:00,340 --> 01:09:02,050
棉花糖一样被拆散了
Pulled us apart like cotton candy.

1027
01:09:02,220 --> 01:09:03,720
你好像没什么大碍嘛
Seems like you walked away all right.

1028
01:09:06,310 --> 01:09:07,310
有问题吗
Is that a problem?

1029
01:09:07,430 --> 01:09:09,690
没有黑暗面的人不值得信任
I don't trust a guy without a dark side.

1030
01:09:10,770 --> 01:09:11,810
就算我老古董吧
Call me old-fashioned.

1031
01:09:11,940 --> 01:09:14,730
那只是你还没见过
Well, let's just say you haven't seen it yet.

1032
01:09:14,900 --> 01:09:17,190
你知道奥创想分裂我们吧
You know Ultron is trying to tear us apart, right?

1033
01:09:17,230 --> 01:09:19,450
你肯定知道
Well, I guess you'd know.

1034
01:09:19,570 --> 01:09:20,900
会不会告诉我们就不一定了
Whether you'd tell us is a bit of a question.

1035
01:09:21,070 --> 01:09:22,200
班纳和我在搞科研
Banner and I were doing research.

1036
01:09:22,240 --> 01:09:24,580
-会对团队有影响  -是会解散团队吧
- That would affect the team. - That would end the team!

1037
01:09:24,660 --> 01:09:25,830
那不正是目的吗
Isn't that the mission?

1038
01:09:25,950 --> 01:09:27,370
不是我们战斗的理由吗
Isn't that the "why we fight"?

1039
01:09:27,410 --> 01:09:29,710
为了结束战斗  为了回家
So we can end the fight. So we get to go home!

1040
01:09:32,920 --> 01:09:35,340
每次有人想在战争开打前取胜
Every time someone tries to win a war before it starts,

1041
01:09:35,420 --> 01:09:38,170
都会牺牲无辜的人  每次都是
innocent people die. Every time.

1042
01:09:40,550 --> 01:09:41,930
真抱歉
I'm sorry.

1043
01:09:41,970 --> 01:09:42,970
斯塔克先生
Mr. Stark...

1044
01:09:43,800 --> 01:09:44,970
克林特说你不会介意的
Clint said you wouldn't mind,

1045
01:09:45,050 --> 01:09:47,600
我家的拖拉机启动不了了
but our tractor doesn't seem to want to start at all.

1046
01:09:47,770 --> 01:09:50,100
-你能不能去...  -没问题  我去看看
- I thought maybe you might... - Yeah, I'll give her a kick.

1047
01:09:53,600 --> 01:09:55,270
别偷我劈的柴
Don't take from my pile.

1048
01:10:05,450 --> 01:10:06,700
好啊亲爱的
Hello, Dear.

1049
01:10:09,500 --> 01:10:10,950
来给我讲讲
Tell me everything.

1050
01:10:12,120 --> 01:10:13,620
哪里不舒服
What ails you?

1051
01:10:13,710 --> 01:10:14,790
行行好
Do me a favor.

1052
01:10:16,880 --> 01:10:18,880
别把它弄活了
Try not to bring it to life.

1053
01:10:19,000 --> 01:10:20,590
巴顿夫人还真是狡猾
Why, Ms. Barton, you little minx.

1054
01:10:20,960 --> 01:10:23,510
我明白了  希尔给你打电话了
I get it. Maria Hill called you, right?

1055
01:10:23,590 --> 01:10:24,930
她有不给你打工的时候吗
Was she ever not working for you?

1056
01:10:24,970 --> 01:10:26,510
人工智能
Artificial intelligence.

1057
01:10:27,470 --> 01:10:29,310
你一点没犹豫
You never even hesitated.

1058
01:10:29,430 --> 01:10:30,810
今天真的很漫长
Look, it's been a really long day,

1059
01:10:30,890 --> 01:10:32,560
有尤金·奥尼尔的小说[同名]那么长
like Eugene O'Neill long,

1060
01:10:32,640 --> 01:10:34,650
来直接说你能解决什么问题
so how's about we skip to the part where you're useful.

1061
01:10:34,770 --> 01:10:37,440
看着我的眼睛  告诉我你会关闭奥创
Look me in the eye and tell me you're going to shut him down.

1062
01:10:37,560 --> 01:10:39,190
你又不是我的局长
You're not the director of me.

1063
01:10:39,320 --> 01:10:41,110
我谁的局长都不是
I'm not the director of anybody.

1064
01:10:41,240 --> 01:10:43,150
我就是个老头子
I'm just an old man

1065
01:10:43,320 --> 01:10:45,490
刚好很关心你
who cares very much about you.

1066
01:10:48,160 --> 01:10:50,120
我是害死复仇者联盟的人
And I'm the man who killed the Avengers.

1067
01:10:51,660 --> 01:10:53,040
我看到了
I saw it.

1068
01:10:53,120 --> 01:10:54,710
我没告诉大伙  没法说
I didn't tell the team. How could I?

1069
01:10:55,960 --> 01:10:57,840
我看到他们都死了  尼克  我感觉到了
I saw them all dead, Nick. I felt it.

1070
01:10:58,170 --> 01:10:59,710
世界也死了
The whole world, too.

1071
01:11:00,090 --> 01:11:01,090
因为我
Because of me.

1072
01:11:02,760 --> 01:11:04,050
我没准备好
I wasn't ready.

1073
01:11:05,300 --> 01:11:06,720
我没尽力
I didn't do all I could.

1074
01:11:07,680 --> 01:11:09,850
这是马克西莫夫的把戏  斯塔克
Maximoff girl, she's working you, Stark.

1075
01:11:10,390 --> 01:11:11,430
利用你的恐惧
Playing on your fear.

1076
01:11:11,520 --> 01:11:13,980
不是把戏  我真看到了
I wasn't tricked, I was shown.

1077
01:11:14,020 --> 01:11:16,270
不是噩梦  是我留给后人的
Wasn't a nightmare, it was my legacy.

1078
01:11:16,400 --> 01:11:18,520
我带着大家走向了死亡
The end of the path I started us on.

1079
01:11:19,650 --> 01:11:22,530
你是发明过不少厉害的玩意  托尼
You come up with some pretty impressive inventions, Tony.

1080
01:11:24,030 --> 01:11:25,610
可战争不是
War isn't one of them.

1081
01:11:28,910 --> 01:11:30,700
我看到朋友死去
I watched my friends die.

1082
01:11:30,740 --> 01:11:33,040
你觉得这够惨了吗
You'd think that'd be as bad as it gets, right?

1083
01:11:34,200 --> 01:11:35,710
还不够
Nope.

1084
01:11:36,620 --> 01:11:38,170
那还不是最坏的
It wasn't the worst part.

1085
01:11:38,210 --> 01:11:39,210
最坏的是
The worst part

1086
01:11:40,130 --> 01:11:41,590
只有你没死
is that you didn't.

1087
01:11:48,220 --> 01:11:49,350
今晚见了
I'll see you tonight.

1088
01:11:50,390 --> 01:11:52,010
{\an8}伦敦  皇家霍罗威大学

1089
01:11:52,060 --> 01:11:53,390
造型不错
I like the look.

1090
01:11:54,350 --> 01:11:57,140
不过想不惹人注意还差点
If you're going for inconspicuous, though, near miss.

1091
01:11:57,310 --> 01:11:58,440
我需要你帮忙
I need your help.

1092
01:11:58,560 --> 01:11:59,730
有人需要真好
It's nice to be needed.

1093
01:11:59,860 --> 01:12:01,230
很危险
It's dangerous.

1094
01:12:01,980 --> 01:12:03,900
不危险我才失望呢
I'd be disappointed if it wasn't.

1095
01:12:06,740 --> 01:12:10,320
奥创把你们赶走  好给自己争取时间
Ultron took you folks out of play to buy himself time.

1096
01:12:10,410 --> 01:12:13,410
我的线人都说他在打造什么
My contacts all say he's building something.

1097
01:12:13,450 --> 01:12:16,040
他弄了那么多振金
The amount of vibranium he made off with,

1098
01:12:16,160 --> 01:12:17,580
应该不止一件
I don't think it's just one thing.

1099
01:12:17,710 --> 01:12:19,170
那奥创呢
What about Ultron himself?

1100
01:12:19,250 --> 01:12:21,750
他好追踪  哪都有他
He's easy to track. He's everywhere.

1101
01:12:21,880 --> 01:12:24,550
他比母猪还高产
The guy is multiplying faster than a Catholic rabbit.

1102
01:12:25,090 --> 01:12:26,150
可还是看不透
It still doesn't help us

1103
01:12:26,150 --> 01:12:27,970
他究竟在计划什么
get an angle on any of his plans, though.

1104
01:12:28,050 --> 01:12:29,390
还想找核弹密码吗
Is he still going after launch codes?

1105
01:12:29,430 --> 01:12:30,800
是啊
Yes, he is.

1106
01:12:30,930 --> 01:12:32,430
可一直没什么进展
But he's not making any headway.

1107
01:12:32,550 --> 01:12:34,560
我高中玩大冒险时就把五角大楼的防火墙破了
I cracked the Pentagon's firewall in high school on a dare.

1108
01:12:34,680 --> 01:12:37,230
我联系了"链结"的朋友
Well, I contacted our friends at the Nexus about that.

1109
01:12:37,350 --> 01:12:38,440
链结
Nexus?

1110
01:12:38,520 --> 01:12:40,440
奥斯陆的互联网中心
It's the world internet hub in Oslo.

1111
01:12:40,560 --> 01:12:42,560
所有联网数据都要经过那里
Every byte of data flows through there.

1112
01:12:42,610 --> 01:12:43,690
全球最快的连接速度
Fastest access on Earth.

1113
01:12:43,770 --> 01:12:44,900
他们怎么说
So, what did they say?

1114
01:12:45,030 --> 01:12:46,900
他认准了核弹
He's fixated on the missiles.

1115
01:12:47,030 --> 01:12:48,780
但密码一直在改
But the codes are constantly being changed.

1116
01:12:49,150 --> 01:12:50,570
谁在改
By whom?

1117
01:12:51,780 --> 01:12:52,780
未知势力
Parties unknown.

1118
01:12:52,870 --> 01:12:54,030
我们有盟友吗
