He will do anything to make things right.

1325
01:26:53,920 --> 01:26:55,250
斯塔克  收到没
Stark, come in.

1326
01:26:55,670 --> 01:26:56,670
斯塔克
Stark.

1327
01:26:58,050 --> 01:26:59,210
有人收到吗
Anyone on comms.

1328
