This is sealed tight.

1334
01:27:15,400 --> 01:27:16,940
得修改程序
We're gonna need to access the program,

1335
01:27:16,980 --> 01:27:18,980
从里面瓦解它
break it down from within.

1336
01:27:20,150 --> 01:27:21,200
娜塔莎有没有可能
Any chance Natasha might

1337
01:27:21,200 --> 01:27:22,990
在互联网之外给你留了线索
leave you a message outside the Internet?

1338
01:27:23,070 --> 01:27:24,110
老派间谍那套吗
Old-school spy stuff?

1339
01:27:24,490 --> 01:27:26,320
