if you could fry whatever operational system Cho implanted.

1343
01:27:35,500 --> 01:27:36,630
这个嘛
Yeah, about that.

1344
01:27:41,010 --> 01:27:42,090
不行
No.

1345
01:27:42,210 --> 01:27:44,130
-你得相信我  -不怎么信呢
- You have to trust me. - Kind of don't.

1346
