I found him.

1348
01:27:51,350 --> 01:27:52,470
你好  班纳博士
Hello, Dr. Banner.

1349
01:27:53,350 --> 01:27:55,600
奥创不是因为愤怒追杀的贾维斯
Ultron didn't go after Jarvis because he was angry.

1350
01:27:56,190 --> 01:27:59,860
他攻击他是因为害怕他的能力
He attacked him because he was scared of what he can do.

1351
01:28:00,940 --> 01:28:02,650
所以贾维斯潜伏了起来
So Jarvis went underground.

1352
01:28:02,690 --> 01:28:04,240
分散开  抛弃了他的记忆
Scattered, dumped his memory.

1353
