01:28:35,980 --> 01:28:37,020
这是机遇
This is the opportunity.

1364
01:28:37,060 --> 01:28:38,850
我们可以造出完美的奥创
We can create Ultron's perfect self

1365
01:28:38,980 --> 01:28:40,070
不会想着灭绝人类
without the homicidal

1366
