Make a stand.

1377
01:29:08,340 --> 01:29:09,930
这不是循环
It's not a loop.

1378
01:29:11,100 --> 01:29:12,930
是走到了终点
It's the end of the line.

1379
01:29:33,370 --> 01:29:35,580
不知道你能不能醒
I wasn't sure you would wake up.

1380
01:29:35,620 --> 01:29:39,120
希望你能醒  想给你看点东西
I hoped you would. I wanted to show you.

1381
