I think a lot about meteors. The purity in them.

1383
01:29:47,460 --> 01:29:49,130
嘣  就完了
Boom! The end.

1384
01:29:49,470 --> 01:29:50,970
重新开始
Start again.

1385
01:29:51,050 --> 01:29:53,010
世界焕然一新
The world made clean

1386
01:29:53,140 --> 01:29:55,470
给新人类重建家园
for the new man to rebuild.

1387
01:29:55,810 --> 01:29:57,980
我注定是新人类
I was meant to be new.

1388
01:29:58,810 --> 01:30:01,440
我注定美妙无比
I was meant to be beautiful.

1389
01:30:01,980 --> 01:30:04,110
世界本可以抬头望天
The world would have looked to the sky

1390
01:30:04,150 --> 01:30:05,480
看到希望
and seen hope,

1391
01:30:05,820 --> 01:30:07,150
看到慈悲
seen mercy.

1392
01:30:07,900 --> 01:30:10,030
可现在他们只会恐惧地抬头看
Instead, they'll look up in horror

1393
01:30:10,110 --> 01:30:11,530
只因为你们
because of you.

1394
