你们伤害了我
You've wounded me.

1395
01:30:14,070 --> 01:30:15,830
这点不得不佩服
I give you full marks for that.

1396
01:30:16,410 --> 01:30:19,410
但是人类总是说  杀不死我的
But, like the man said, what doesn't kill me...

1397
01:30:24,500 --> 01:30:25,920
只会让我更强大
...just makes me stronger.

1398
01:31:06,000 --> 01:31:08,210
这套框架不匹配
This framework is not compatible.

1399
01:31:08,300 --> 01:31:11,050
基因编码已经完成了97%
The genetic coding tower is at 97%.

1400
01:31:11,090 --> 01:31:15,010
还剩三分钟  得赶紧把程序传上去
You have got to upload that schematic in the next three minutes.

1401
01:31:17,260 --> 01:31:19,220
-我只说一次  -一次也不说怎么样
- I'm gonna say this once. - How about "None-ce"?

1402
01:31:19,350 --> 01:31:21,390
-关掉  -不行  不可能
- Shut it down! - Nope, not gonna happen.

1403
01:31:21,480 --> 01:31:22,640
你不知道自己在做什么
You don't know what you're doing.

1404
01:31:22,770 --> 01:31:24,140
你知道吗
And you do?

1405
01:31:24,480 --> 01:31:25,520
她没进入你的意识吗
She's not in your head?

1406
01:31:25,650 --> 01:31:27,310
我知道你很生气
I know you're angry.

1407
01:31:27,440 --> 01:31:28,860
远不止是生气呢
We're way past that.

1408
01:31:28,900 --> 01:31:31,360
我不用变绿都能掐死你
I could choke the life out of you and never change a shade.

1409
01:31:31,490 --> 01:31:33,110
班纳  发生了这么多...
Banner, after everything that's happened...

1410
01:31:33,200 --> 01:31:34,740
将要发生的事才最重要
It's nothing compared to what's coming!

1411
01:31:34,860 --> 01:31:36,320
-你不知道里面有什么  -这不是游戏
- You don't know what's in there. - This isn't a game!

1412
01:31:40,490 --> 01:31:41,910
别  别  继续
No, no. Go on.

1413
01:31:42,790 --> 01:31:44,080
你说什么
You were saying?

1414
01:31:50,630 --> 01:31:52,010
皮特
Pietro!

1415
01:31:52,720 --> 01:31:53,720
怎么
What?

1416
01:31:54,090 --> 01:31:55,760
没预见到吗
You didn't see that coming?

1417
01:31:55,790 --> 01:31:56,760
{\an8}电力损失过度

1418
01:31:57,850 --> 01:31:59,050
我换条线路上传
I'm rerouting the upload.

1419
01:32:05,940 --> 01:32:07,100
来啊  惹我生气吧
Go ahead, piss me off.

1420
01:32:19,370 --> 01:32:20,780
等等
Wait!

1421
01:33:45,200 --> 01:33:47,540
抱歉  刚真是
I am sorry. That was

1422
01:33:48,500 --> 01:33:49,920
奇怪
odd.

1423
01:33:50,080 --> 01:33:51,420
谢谢
Thank you.

1424
01:33:56,340 --> 01:33:57,340
托尔
Thor.

1425
01:33:58,760 --> 01:33:59,800
你帮忙创造了他吗
You helped create this?

1426
01:33:59,930 --> 01:34:01,430
我看到了未来
I've had a vision.

1427
01:34:01,550 --> 01:34:03,940
所有生命的希望都被个漩涡吸走
A whirlpool that sucks in all hope of life,

1428
01:34:03,940 --> 01:34:05,390
漩涡的中心就是那个
and at its center is that.

1429
01:34:06,310 --> 01:34:07,390
什么   宝石吗
What? The gem?

1430
01:34:07,430 --> 01:34:08,520
是意识宝石
It's the Mind Stone.

1431
01:34:08,560 --> 01:34:10,060
六颗无限宝石之一
It's one of the six Infinity Stones.

1432
01:34:10,230 --> 01:34:11,520
宇宙里最强大的力量
The greatest power in the universe,

1433
01:34:11,560 --> 01:34:13,810
毁灭能力无可比拟
unparalleled in its destructive capabilities.

1434
01:34:13,900 --> 01:34:15,900
-那你为什么还...  -因为斯塔克是对的
- Then why would you bring... - Because Stark is right.

1435
01:34:16,030 --> 01:34:18,530
这下可真是毁了
It's definitely the end times.

1436
01:34:18,650 --> 01:34:19,740
复仇者联盟赢不了奥创的
The Avengers cannot defeat Ultron.

1437
01:34:19,820 --> 01:34:21,160
光靠自己不行
Not alone.

1438
01:34:21,610 --> 01:34:23,620
为什么幻视的声音像贾维斯
Why does your Vision sound like Jarvis?

1439
01:34:23,700 --> 01:34:26,370
我们重构了贾维斯的程序
We reconfigured Jarvis's matrix

1440
01:34:26,830 --> 01:34:28,700
创造了新的东西
to create something new.

1441
01:34:28,870 --> 01:34:30,620
新东西我真是看够了
I think I've had my fill of new.

1442
01:34:30,710 --> 01:34:33,040
你觉得我是奥创的孩子
You think I'm a child of Ultron.

1443
01:34:33,330 --> 01:34:34,670
不是吗
You're not?

1444
01:34:35,750 --> 01:34:37,420
我不是奥创
I'm not Ultron.

1445
01:34:37,960 --> 01:34:40,260
我不是贾维斯  我是
I am not Jarvis. I am...

1446
01:34:42,300 --> 01:34:43,760
这个我
I am.

1447
01:34:45,600 --> 01:34:46,760
我看过你的意识
I looked in your head

1448
01:34:47,430 --> 01:34:49,270
看到了大灭绝
and saw annihilation.

1449
01:34:49,430 --> 01:34:50,430
再看看
Look again.

1450
01:34:50,850 --> 01:34:52,350
她赞同顶个屁啊
Her seal of approval means jack to me.

1451
01:34:52,850 --> 01:34:55,610
他们的力量  我们的恐惧  包括奥创
Their powers, the horrors in our heads, Ultron himself,

1452
01:34:55,690 --> 01:34:57,110
