they all came from the Mind Stone.

1453
01:34:57,230 --> 01:34:59,440
这跟宝石的力量比都不算什么
And they're nothing compared to what it can unleash.

1454
01:34:59,570 --> 01:35:01,070
-可如果在我们这边...  -是吗
- But with it on our side... - Is it?

1455
01:35:02,490 --> 01:35:03,740
你是吗
Are you?

1456
01:35:04,530 --> 01:35:05,950
在我们这边
On our side?

1457
