我觉得没那么简单
I don't think it's that simple.

1458
01:35:09,870 --> 01:35:12,410
最好赶紧弄简单点
Well, it better get real simple real soon.

1459
01:35:13,500 --> 01:35:15,670
我站在生命这边
I am on the side of life.

1460
01:35:15,830 --> 01:35:17,290
奥创不是
Ultron isn't.

1461
01:35:17,800 --> 01:35:19,300
他会毁灭生命
He will end it all.

1462
