-你  -在哪
- You. - Where?

1464
01:35:22,880 --> 01:35:24,090
索科威亚
Sokovia.

1465
01:35:24,220 --> 01:35:25,300
小娜也关在那
He's got Nat there, too.

1466
01:35:27,390 --> 01:35:29,060
如果我们看错了你
If we're wrong about you,

1467
01:35:31,730 --> 01:35:33,560
如果你是奥创造出来的怪物
if you're the monster that Ultron made you to be...

1468
01:35:34,230 --> 01:35:35,850
你会怎么做
What will you do?

1469
01:35:42,400 --> 01:35:44,570
我不想杀奥创
I don't want to kill Ultron.

1470
01:35:44,860 --> 01:35:48,280
他很独特  很痛苦
He's unique and he's in pain.

1471
01:35:49,790 --> 01:35:52,540
但那痛苦会毁灭地球
But that pain will roll over the Earth.

1472
01:35:52,710 --> 01:35:55,290
所以必须毁灭他
So, he must be destroyed.

1473
01:35:55,420 --> 01:35:58,460
他的每一个形态  留下的每一丝痕迹
Every form he's built, every trace of his presence on the net.

1474
01:35:58,590 --> 01:36:00,460
现在就得行动
We have to act now.

1475
01:36:00,630 --> 01:36:04,630
这点我们光靠自己是做不到的
And not one of us can do it without the others.

1476
01:36:06,640 --> 01:36:08,510
我也许是个怪物
Maybe I am a monster.

1477
01:36:08,680 --> 01:36:11,020
我是不是自己也不会知道
I don't think I'd know if I were one.

1478
01:36:12,140 --> 01:36:13,730
我不是你们
I'm not what you are,

1479
01:36:14,350 --> 01:36:16,600
也不是你们希望的那样
and not what you intended.

1480
01:36:17,270 --> 01:36:19,820
你们也许不会相信我
So, there may be no way to make you trust me.

1481
01:36:20,020 --> 01:36:21,530
但我们得走了
But we need to go.

1482
01:36:36,250 --> 01:36:37,500
好吧
Right.

1483
01:36:38,040 --> 01:36:39,380
漂亮
Well done.

1484
01:36:41,050 --> 01:36:42,090
三分钟
Three minutes.

1485
01:36:42,840 --> 01:36:44,510
准备妥当吧
Get what you need.

1486
01:36:56,300 --> 01:36:57,400
{\an8}星期五

1487
01:37:00,400 --> 01:37:01,400
晚上好  老大
Good evening, boss.

1488
01:37:06,530 --> 01:37:08,160
我们不可能都撑过来的
No way we all get through this.

1489
01:37:08,280 --> 01:37:10,240
那怕还有一个铁人在  我们都输了
If even one tin soldier is left standing, we've lost.

1490
01:37:11,080 --> 01:37:12,450
肯定会流血的
There's gonna be blood on the floor.

1491
01:37:12,580 --> 01:37:13,950
我明晚是没安排
I got no plans tomorrow night.

1492
01:37:14,040 --> 01:37:15,250
大家伙先给我打
I get first crack at the big guy.

1493
01:37:15,830 --> 01:37:17,410
他等的是钢铁侠
Iron Man's the one he's waiting for.

1494
01:37:17,460 --> 01:37:19,920
没错  他最恨你
That's true. He hates you the most.

1495
01:37:25,210 --> 01:37:27,470
奥创知道我们要去
Ultron knows we're coming.

1496
01:37:27,590 --> 01:37:29,800
他们很可能已经严阵以待
Odds are we'll be riding into heavy fire.

1497
01:37:30,300 --> 01:37:32,100
我们早为这一刻做好了准备
And that's what we signed up for.

1498
01:37:32,260 --> 01:37:35,100
但索科威亚的人民没有
But the people of Sokovia, they didn't.

1499
01:37:35,970 --> 01:37:37,520
当务之急
