Let's load them up.

1691
01:52:14,940 --> 01:52:18,820
长官  右舷纠集了数架敌机
Sir, we have multiple bogies converging on our starboard flank.

1692
01:52:19,110 --> 01:52:20,320
给他们点颜色
Show 'em what we got.

1693
01:52:20,730 --> 01:52:21,740
上吧
You're up.

1694
01:52:26,950 --> 01:52:27,990
棒
Yes!

1695
01:52:28,160 --> 01:52:29,950
这回可有的讲了
Now this is gonna be a good story.

1696
01:52:32,580 --> 01:52:34,670
是啊  但你得先活下来
Yup. If you live to tell it.

1697
01:52:34,790 --> 01:52:36,880
你觉得我自己办不到[握我自己的]吗
You think I can't hold my own?

1698
