到你嘴里就变了味
You had to make it weird.

1700
01:52:45,340 --> 01:52:48,350
这群人之后还有50到100个
I got about 50 to 100 more coming in after this group.

1701
01:53:05,200 --> 01:53:06,700
快走  快走  走吧
Here we go. Here we go. Let's move.

1702
01:53:07,070 --> 01:53:08,070
快走
Let's go, everyone!

1703
01:53:10,580 --> 01:53:12,660
{\an8}Lock, stock and barrel

1704
01:53:10,580 --> 01:53:12,660
六号舱已全部  锁定...
Number six boat is topped and locked...

1705
01:53:12,700 --> 01:53:15,160
全员...  到头...
Or stocked... Topped...

1706
01:53:15,660 --> 01:53:17,080
人已经满了
It's full of people.

1707
01:53:18,830 --> 01:53:19,920
敌机来袭
Incoming!

1708
01:53:22,920 --> 01:53:24,050
我的天
Oh, God!

1709
01:53:34,520 --> 01:53:35,770
你觉得你能救谁吗
You think you're saving anyone?

1710
01:53:37,600 --> 01:53:39,940
我转一下  早一点让这座城掉下去
I turn that key and drop this rock a little early

1711
01:53:40,020 --> 01:53:41,900
还是会死伤上亿
and it's still billions dead.

1712
01:53:42,320 --> 01:53:43,440
连你也不能阻止
Even you can't stop that.

1713
01:53:43,570 --> 01:53:46,200
我是托尔  奥丁之子
I am Thor, son of Odin,

1714
01:53:46,240 --> 01:53:48,490
只要我还有一口气...
and as long as there is life in my breast...

1715
01:53:48,660 --> 01:53:51,080
我想不出词了
I am running out of things to say!

1716
01:53:51,160 --> 01:53:52,160
准备好了吗
Are you ready?

1717
01:53:59,830 --> 01:54:00,960
这锤子重量分布得真好
It's terribly well-balanced.

1718
01:54:01,340 --> 01:54:03,060
要是锤头太重
Well, if there's too much weight,

1719
01:54:03,060 --> 01:54:04,840
挥起来会损失力量  所以...
you lose power on the swing, so...

1720
01:54:05,760 --> 01:54:08,470
有了  弄个热能护罩
I got it. Create a heat seal.

1721
01:54:08,840 --> 01:54:09,840
我可以...
I could...

1722
01:54:09,970 --> 01:54:12,350
我可以在底下让装置过载
I could supercharge the spire from below.

1723
01:54:12,470 --> 01:54:13,720
计算中
Running numbers.

1724
01:54:23,730 --> 01:54:25,780
能量够的话  热护罩可以成功
A heat seal could work with enough power.

1725
01:54:25,860 --> 01:54:27,860
-托尔  我有计划了  -没时间了
- Thor, I got a plan. - We're out of time.

1726
01:54:27,990 --> 01:54:29,320
他们冲着核心来了
They're coming for the core.

1727
01:54:29,410 --> 01:54:31,280
罗德  送其他人上救生舱
Rhodey, get the rest of the people on board that carrier.

1728
01:54:31,320 --> 01:54:32,320
好的
On it.

1729
01:54:32,410 --> 01:54:34,620
复仇者  该搏回命了
Avengers, time to work for a living.

1730
01:54:43,630 --> 01:54:44,960
-没事吧  -没事
- Are you good? - Yeah.

1731
01:54:46,380 --> 01:54:47,460
罗曼诺夫
Romanoff.

1732
01:54:47,630 --> 01:54:50,130
你和班纳不是打算鸳鸯双飞  一起隐居吧
You and Banner better not be playing "hide the zucchini."

1733
01:54:50,180 --> 01:54:51,180
别激动  铁头
Relax, shellhead.

1734
01:54:51,510 --> 01:54:53,050
还有人不会飞呢
Not all of us can fly.

1735
01:54:58,730 --> 01:55:00,480
-你什么打算[钻头]  -这就是
- What's the drill? - This is the drill.

1736
01:55:00,560 --> 01:55:02,770
让奥创碰到核心  我们就失败了
If Ultron gets a hand on the core, we lose.

1737
01:55:07,320 --> 01:55:09,320
你们就这点能耐吗
Is that the best you can do?

1738
01:55:19,200 --> 01:55:20,750
非得好心问一下
You had to ask.

1739
01:55:20,870 --> 01:55:23,290
这就是我的能耐
This is the best I can do.

1740
01:55:23,330 --> 01:55:25,000
我就想这样
This is exactly what I wanted.

1741
01:55:25,340 --> 01:55:26,670
你们所有人
All of you

1742
01:55:26,840 --> 01:55:28,510
对阵所有的我
against all of me.

1743
01:55:28,670 --> 01:55:30,880
你们怎么可能阻止我
How can you possibly hope to stop me?

1744
01:55:31,680 --> 01:55:33,640
老爷子说过...
Well, like the old man said...

1745
01:55:34,930 --> 01:55:35,970
齐心协力
together.

1746
01:57:04,890 --> 01:57:07,310
我事后诸葛亮一下...
You know, with the benefit of hindsight...

1747
01:57:16,490 --> 01:57:17,610
他们想逃离城市
They'll try to leave the city.

1748
01:57:17,700 --> 01:57:19,410
不可以  一个也不能放  罗德
We can't let them, not even one. Rhodey.

1749
01:57:19,830 --> 01:57:20,830
收到
I'm on it.

1750
01:57:21,240 --> 01:57:22,620
没让你走呢
No. I didn't say you could leave.

1751
01:57:23,200 --> 01:57:25,370
战争机器来了  就在...
War Machine coming at you! Right...

1752
01:57:31,670 --> 01:57:33,130
这是什么
Okay, what?

1753
01:57:33,300 --> 01:57:35,380
得撤了  我都能感觉到空气变稀薄了
We gotta move out. Even I can tell the air is getting thin.

1754
01:57:35,470 --> 01:57:36,800
你们去救生舱
You guys get to the boats.

1755
01:57:36,880 --> 01:57:38,680
我再找一下有没有漏的  一会找你们
I'll sweep for stragglers. Be right behind you.

1756
01:57:38,800 --> 01:57:40,220
核心呢
What about the core?

1757
01:57:40,390 --> 01:57:41,390
我来保护
I'll protect it.

1758
01:57:43,310 --> 01:57:44,310
这是我的职责
It's my job.

1759
01:57:45,520 --> 01:57:46,520
小娜
Nat.

1760
01:57:46,850 --> 01:57:47,900
这边
This way.

1761
01:57:52,270 --> 01:57:53,570
带人们上救生舱
Get the people on the boats.

1762
01:57:53,650 --> 01:57:54,650
我不能把你留在这
I'm not going to leave you here.

1763
01:57:54,740 --> 01:57:55,860
我能应付这个
I can handle this.

1764
01:57:58,110 --> 01:57:59,410
等大家都撤了再回来
Come back for me when everyone else is off.

1765
01:57:59,530 --> 01:58:00,700
一个也不能少
Not before.

1766
01:58:01,280 --> 01:58:02,830
明白吗
You understand?

1767
01:58:03,830 --> 01:58:05,540
我可是比你大了12分钟
You know, I'm 12 minutes older than you.

1768
01:58:05,750 --> 01:58:07,040
去吧
Go.

1769
01:58:08,620 --> 01:58:10,170
老大  能量已经远低于...
Boss, power levels are way below...

1770
01:58:10,210 --> 01:58:12,420
重新分配能源  只有一次机会
Reroute everything. We get one shot at this.

1771
01:58:17,300 --> 01:58:18,630
我知道需要干什么
I know what I need to do.

1772
01:58:18,930 --> 01:58:20,010
餐厅
The dining room.

1773
01:58:20,300 --> 01:58:21,510
把东面的墙拆掉
If I knock out that east wall,

1774
01:58:22,180 --> 01:58:23,720
劳拉就有了工作的地方
it'd make a nice workspace for Laura, huh?

1775
01:58:25,270 --> 01:58:26,520
周围挡一下
Put up some baffling.

1776
01:58:26,560 --> 01:58:28,690
她听不到孩子们乱跑的  怎么样
She can't hear the kids running around. What do you think?

1777
01:58:28,770 --> 01:58:30,060
反正你们总在厨房吃
You guys always eat in the kitchen anyway.

1778
01:58:30,150 --> 01:58:31,730
谁在餐厅吃饭啊
No one eats in a dining room.

1779
01:58:37,400 --> 01:58:38,450
时间不多了
We don't have a lot of time.

1780
01:58:39,030 --> 01:58:41,070
赶紧上救生舱
So get your ass on a boat.

1781
01:58:53,960 --> 01:58:55,170
大家伙
Hey, big guy.

1782
01:58:56,880 --> 01:58:58,670
太阳就要下山了
Sun's getting real low.

1783
01:58:59,220 --> 01:59:01,890
你安全了  没事的  系好安全带
You're safe now. You're gonna be okay. Buckle up.

1784
01:59:04,390 --> 01:59:06,020
保管好自己的物品  抓紧就坐
Secure your gear, find a seat.

1785
01:59:06,060 --> 01:59:07,390
科斯特尔
Costel!

1786
01:59:08,390 --> 01:59:09,640
我们之前一起在市场
We were in the market.

1787
01:59:09,770 --> 01:59:10,810
科斯特尔
Costel!

1788
01:59:25,410 --> 01:59:27,450
托尔  我需要你回教堂
Thor, I'm gonna need you back in the church.

1789
01:59:27,620 --> 01:59:29,080
-就这些人了吗  -嗯
- Is this the last of them? - Yeah.

1790
01:59:29,460 --> 01:59:30,500
其他人都上航母了
Everyone else is on the carrier.

1791
01:59:30,580 --> 01:59:31,750
如果这次成功了
You know, this works,

1792
01:59:32,370 --> 01:59:33,750
我们可能活不下来
we maybe don't walk away.

1793
01:59:34,460 --> 01:59:35,540
没准吧
Maybe not.

1794
01:59:54,690 --> 01:59:58,280
没有了束缚  我开心地玩
I got no strings, so I have fun

1795
01:59:58,690 --> 02:00:01,490
不被任何人约束
I'm not tied up to anyone

1796
02:00:02,950 --> 02:00:04,320
快点  走吧
Come on. Time to go.

1797
02:00:36,770 --> 02:00:38,860
你没预见到吗
You didn't see that coming?

1798
02:01:35,040 --> 02:01:36,870
我的天呐
For God's sake.

1799
02:01:53,060 --> 02:01:54,930
-泽林卡  -科斯特尔  宝贝
- Zrinka! - Costel! Baby!

1800
02:02:07,320 --> 02:02:08,360
不  不  我没事
No, no, I'm fine.

1801
02:02:08,490 --> 02:02:09,570
没事
Fine.

1802
02:02:11,410 --> 02:02:13,490
今天真是漫长
It's been a long day.

1803
02:02:27,970 --> 02:02:29,260
旺达
Wanda.

1804
02:02:29,930 --> 02:02:33,220
你留在这会死的
If you stay here, you'll die.

1805
02:02:34,720 --> 02:02:36,180
我刚死过
I just did.

1806
02:02:36,930 --> 02:02:38,640
你知道什么感觉吗
Do you know how it felt?

1807
02:02:52,780 --> 02:02:55,080
就这种感觉
It felt like that.

1808
02:03:30,070 --> 02:03:31,740
托尔  等我口令
Thor, on my mark.

1809
02:03:46,840 --> 02:03:47,840
动手
Now!

1810
02:04:15,870 --> 02:04:18,240
大家伙  我们成功了
Hey, big guy. We did it.

1811
02:04:19,290 --> 02:04:20,950
任务完成了
The job is finished.

1812
02:04:21,210 --> 02:04:23,870
现在你得驾驶飞机返航
Now I need you to turn this bird around, okay?

1813
02:04:28,130 --> 02:04:29,960
隐匿模式追踪不到你
We can't track you in stealth mode.

1814
02:04:32,050 --> 02:04:34,300
帮我个忙  我需要你...
So help me out. I need you...

1815
02:05:19,890 --> 02:05:20,970
你怕了
You're afraid.

1816
02:05:21,890 --> 02:05:22,930
怕你吗
Of you?

1817
02:05:23,640 --> 02:05:24,890
怕死亡
Of death.

1818
02:05:25,520 --> 02:05:27,400
你是最后一个
You're the last one.

1819
02:05:27,560 --> 02:05:30,110
你本该是最后一个
You were supposed to be the last.

1820
02:05:30,270 --> 02:05:32,610
斯塔克想造救世主
Stark asked for a savior

1821
02:05:33,530 --> 02:05:35,280
却甘心得到个奴隶
and settled for a slave.

1822
02:05:35,360 --> 02:05:37,870
看来我们都让人失望了
I suppose we are both disappointments.

1823
02:05:40,200 --> 02:05:41,450
是啊
I suppose we are.

1824
02:05:42,200 --> 02:05:43,370
人类真奇怪
Humans are odd.

1825
02:05:45,210 --> 02:05:48,920
他们觉得秩序与混乱是相对的
They think order and chaos are somehow opposites

1826
02:05:50,590 --> 02:05:51,960
想控制自己无力掌控的
and try to control what won't be.

1827
02:05:53,630 --> 02:05:56,130
但他们的努力值得尊敬
But there is grace in their failings.

1828
02:05:56,470 --> 02:05:58,430
你没注意到吧
I think you missed that.

1829
02:05:59,010 --> 02:06:00,180
他们注定灭亡
They're doomed.

1830
02:06:01,010 --> 02:06:02,140
是啊
Yes.

1831
02:06:06,270 --> 02:06:09,270
但事物的美  并不在能否长久
But a thing isn't beautiful because it lasts.

1832
02:06:11,270 --> 02:06:13,360
身为他们的一员很荣幸
It's a privilege to be among them.

1833
02:06:13,480 --> 02:06:16,110
你真是天真到无可救药
You're unbearably naive.

1834
02:06:16,320 --> 02:06:17,610
这个嘛
Well...

1835
02:06:19,620 --> 02:06:21,740
毕竟我昨天才出生
I was born yesterday.

1836
02:07:11,830 --> 02:07:15,880
{\an8}纽约州北部  新复仇者联盟总部

1837
02:07:34,230 --> 02:07:35,320
{\an8}内特尼尔·皮特·巴顿

1838
02:07:34,230 --> 02:07:35,320
看  来见见小娜阿姨
Look! Say hi to Auntie Nat!

1839
02:07:37,740 --> 02:07:38,820
胖墩
Fat.

1840
02:07:39,900 --> 02:07:41,110
有个技术员标记了这个
One of our tech boys flagged this.

1841
02:07:42,160 --> 02:07:44,450
在班达海[印尼]坠毁了
Splashed down in the Banda Sea.

1842
02:07:45,620 --> 02:07:47,120
可能是昆式战机
Could be the Quinjet.

1843
02:07:47,490 --> 02:07:49,050
但是有斯塔克的隐匿技术
But with Stark's stealth tech,

1844
02:07:49,050 --> 02:07:50,910
我们根本搜索不到
we still can't track the damn thing.

1845
02:07:52,420 --> 02:07:53,830
好吧
Right.

1846
02:07:54,210 --> 02:07:56,460
有可能跳机游到了斐济
Probably jumped out and swam to Fiji.

1847
02:07:57,760 --> 02:07:59,670
他会寄明信片的
He'll send a postcard.

1848
02:07:59,920 --> 02:08:01,680
"真希望你在这"
"Wish you were here."

1849
02:08:03,590 --> 02:08:06,810
当初是你派我招募的他
You sent me to recruit him way back when.

1850
02:08:08,680 --> 02:08:11,270
你那时知道会发生什么吗
Did you know then what was gonna happen?

1851
02:08:13,440 --> 02:08:15,440
怎么可能知道
You never know.

1852
02:08:15,610 --> 02:08:19,110
只能先尽人事  再听天命了
You hope for the best, then make do with what you get.

1853
02:08:19,570 --> 02:08:20,990
我的团队不错
I got a great team.

1854
02:08:22,150 --> 02:08:24,160
没什么是永久的
Nothing lasts forever.

1855
02:08:24,450 --> 02:08:26,530
麻烦永远在  罗曼诺夫小姐
Trouble, Ms. Romanoff.

1856
02:08:26,700 --> 02:08:30,040
不管谁赢谁输  麻烦总是免不了的
No matter who wins or loses, trouble still comes around.

1857
02:08:33,960 --> 02:08:35,210
规则已经变了
The rules have changed.

1858
02:08:35,330 --> 02:08:36,920
这是个新东西
We're dealing with something new.

1859
02:08:37,040 --> 02:08:38,460
幻视是人工智能
The Vision is artificial intelligence.

1860
02:08:38,500 --> 02:08:40,510
-一台机器  -所以不算吗
- A machine. - So, it doesn't count?

1861
02:08:40,590 --> 02:08:42,380
举锤子的不是个人
No, it's not like a person lifting the hammer.

1862
02:08:42,680 --> 02:08:44,430
是啊  到我们这就不一样了
Right, different rules for us.

1863
02:08:44,470 --> 02:08:45,510
-他是个好人  人造的  -谢谢
- Nice guy. Artificial. - Thank you.

1864
02:08:45,640 --> 02:08:48,600
他能举起锤子  就有资格留着意识宝石
He can wield the hammer, he can keep the Mind Stone.

1865
02:08:49,600 --> 02:08:51,770
宝石在幻视那很安全
It's safe with the Vision.

1866
02:08:51,930 --> 02:08:54,480
这年头安全可不好找
And these days, safe is in short supply.

1867
02:08:56,480 --> 02:08:58,480
可是要是放在电梯里
But if you put the hammer in an elevator...

1868
02:08:58,610 --> 02:09:00,360
-锤子会被举起来  -电梯配不上呢
- It would still go up. - Elevator's not worthy.

1869
02:09:00,480 --> 02:09:02,360
我会怀念你俩的贫嘴的
I'm gonna miss these little talks of ours.

1870
02:09:02,440 --> 02:09:04,110
不走就不会
Not if you don't leave.

1871
02:09:04,150 --> 02:09:06,030
我没得选
I have no choice.

1872
02:09:06,160 --> 02:09:08,370
意识宝石是过去几年
The Mind Stone is the fourth of the Infinity Stones

1873
02:09:08,490 --> 02:09:09,870
出现的第四颗无限宝石
to show up in the last few years.

1874
02:09:09,990 --> 02:09:11,620
绝不是巧合
It's not a coincidence.

1875
02:09:12,370 --> 02:09:14,210
有人在下一盘大棋
Someone has been playing an intricate game

1876
02:09:14,290 --> 02:09:16,000
把我们当棋子
and has made pawns of us.

1877
02:09:16,040 --> 02:09:17,920
如果所有宝石都就位了
And once all these pieces are in position...

1878
02:09:18,040 --> 02:09:19,550
三个大同花
Triple Yahtzee.

1879
02:09:19,670 --> 02:09:21,130
你觉得你能查明怎么回事吗
You think you can find out what's coming?

1880
02:09:21,260 --> 02:09:22,340
能
I do.

1881
02:09:23,090 --> 02:09:24,680
除了这家伙
Besides this one,

1882
02:09:24,760 --> 02:09:27,090
没有解释不了的东西
there's nothing that can't be explained.

1883
02:09:34,440 --> 02:09:36,980
这人真不懂得爱护草坪
That man has no regard for lawn maintenance.

1884
02:09:40,110 --> 02:09:42,820
我倒是会怀念他的  你也会想我的
I'm gonna miss him, though. And you're gonna miss me.

1885
02:09:42,860 --> 02:09:44,610
男子汉这回要掉不少泪呢
There's gonna be a lot of manful tears.

1886
02:09:46,610 --> 02:09:48,370
我会想你的  托尼
I will miss you, Tony.

1887
02:09:48,530 --> 02:09:49,530
是吗
Yeah?

1888
02:09:49,660 --> 02:09:52,240
我是该撤了
Well, it's time for me to tap out.

1889
02:09:52,330 --> 02:09:54,580
我也许应该跟巴顿学点经验
Maybe I should take a page out of Barton's book.

1890
02:09:54,660 --> 02:09:57,670
给小辣椒建个农场  希望没人去炸
Build Pepper a farm, hope nobody blows it up.

1891
02:09:58,290 --> 02:09:59,540
简单的生活
The simple life.

1892
02:09:59,710 --> 02:10:01,050
你会有那天的
You'll get there one day.

1893
02:10:01,090 --> 02:10:02,090
我也不知道
I don't know.

1894
02:10:02,340 --> 02:10:04,800
成家  稳定...
Family, stability...

1895
02:10:05,880 --> 02:10:09,090
渴望那些的我75年前被冻进冰块里了
The guy who wanted all that went in the ice 75 years ago.

1896
02:10:10,510 --> 02:10:12,390
出来的是另一个我了
I think someone else came out.

1897
02:10:16,440 --> 02:10:17,440
你还好吧
You all right?

1898
02:10:20,110 --> 02:10:21,570
我到家了
I'm home.

1899
02:10:29,450 --> 02:10:32,240
你是想盯着墙看还是想去工作
You wanna keep staring at the wall, or do you wanna go to work?

1900
02:10:32,410 --> 02:10:33,790
那堵墙是挺有意思的
I mean, it's a pretty interesting wall.

1901
02:10:33,870 --> 02:10:36,960
你不是和托尼深情对视呢吗
I thought you and Tony were still gazing into each other's eyes.

1902
02:10:37,040 --> 02:10:38,040
怎么样
How do we look?

1903
02:10:38,250 --> 02:10:40,580
反正算不上传奇队伍
Well, we're not the '27 Yankees.

1904
02:10:40,670 --> 02:10:42,460
还是有几个大牌的
We got some hitters.

1905
02:10:42,540 --> 02:10:45,050
是不错  但还不是团队
They're good. They're not a team.

1906
02:10:45,090 --> 02:10:46,720
来调教一下他们吧
Let's beat them into shape.

1907
02:11:05,190 --> 02:11:06,820
复仇者...
Avengers...

1908
02:13:25,580 --> 02:13:27,080
好吧
Fine.

1909
02:13:27,580 --> 02:13:29,080
我自己来
I'll do it myself.

